doc:
Provides a reference to the element at the given index.

Element at index 0 is the front of the queue.

# Examples

```
use std::collections::VecDeque;

let mut buf = VecDeque::new();
buf.push_back(3);
buf.push_back(4);
buf.push_back(5);
buf.push_back(6);
assert_eq!(buf.get(1), Some(&4));
```
